00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:04.970
I looked online and I saw a spot about a half
a mile away from my house that was 4 and a

00:01:04.970 --> 00:01:07.000
half stars, 88 reviews, 4 and a half stars.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:08.670
