00:01:08.670 --> 00:01:12.759
So we went to this place and I'm sitting there
and the waiter comes.

00:01:12.759 --> 00:01:18.090
The waiter comes, and he's standing a foot
away from me, getting ready to take the order.

00:01:18.090 --> 00:01:22.299
