00:02:21.470 --> 00:02:23.470
I eat sushi twice a week.

00:02:23.470 --> 00:02:26.100
The other sushi spot that I like to go to
is 4 1/2 miles away from my house.

00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:27.470
This is a half a mile away from my house.

00:02:27.470 --> 00:02:28.470
Watch this.

00:02:28.470 --> 00:02:29.470
$121.

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:33.050
Let's just say that I go there once a week.

00:02:33.050 --> 00:02:35.380
$121 times 52 weeks in a year.

00:02:35.380 --> 00:02:36.510
You know how much money that is?

00:02:36.510 --> 00:02:45.680
It' roughly $6300 per year.

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:52.750
If I go there for five years, five times $6300,
that's $31,000 they lost over a five-year

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:54.290
period.

