00:03:16.900 --> 00:03:18.670
Their imagination goes to a whole different
place.

00:03:18.670 --> 00:03:19.870
So #1 is cigarettes.

00:03:19.870 --> 00:03:23.510
In sales, if somebody comes to my house and
